    public class GaStepImpl
extends GaScenarioImpl
implements GaStep
    An implementation of the model object 'Ga Step'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Is Atomic
    • Block T
    • Rep
    • Prob
    • Priority
    • Concur Res
    • Host
    • Serv Demand
    • Serv Count
    • Self Delay
    • Scenario
    • Child Scenario
